data.description: Tons of square footage for the whole family AND the driveway to park them!  You will love the easy care tile in high traffic areas and the huge fenced backyard for the furry friends. You could easily enclose the flex room or formal dining room and make a private office. Majority of the home has been wired with CAT6e so excellent internet service throughout. This area is highly desirable for its proximity to major roads and shopping. Roof replaced in 2018. Hot water heater 2020.
